            <head>"The Black Finger"</head>
            <lg part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
               <l enjamb="no" part="N">I have just seen a most beautiful thing</l>
               <l enjamb="no" part="N">Slim and still,</l>
               <l enjamb="no" part="N">Against a gold, gold sky,</l>
               <l enjamb="no" part="N">A straight black cypress,</l>
               <l enjamb="no" part="N">Sensitive,</l>
               <l enjamb="no" part="N">Exquisite,</l>
               <l enjamb="no" part="N">A black finger</l>
               <l enjamb="no" part="N">Pointing upwards.</l>
               <l enjamb="no" part="N">Why, beautiful still finger, are you black?</l>
               <l enjamb="no" part="N">And why are you pointing upwards?</l>
            </lg>
            <byline>-Angelina Grimke</byline>
         </div>
